pe的电视之类的电视也为专辑提供了额外的制作和贡献。</p><p>根据新闻稿，“ Thee Black Boltz”是“向Adebimpe倾向于写和唱人类状况的倾向 - 在其所有形式的所有形式下，在其所有压力下，无论大小都很小。” “ Thee Black Boltz”定于4月18日通过Sub Pop发布。您可以<a href="https://prescriptionpr.createsend1.com/t/j-l-wlkdilk-iyuukkjddt-t/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3832687" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832687" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832687" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Tunde Adebimpe“ Thee Black Boltz”专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tunde-Adebimpe-Thee-Black-Boltz-Album-Artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832687" class="wp-caption-text"> Tunde Adebimpe“ Thee Black Boltz”专辑艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>Tunde Adebimp的“ Thee Thee Black Boltz”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1。&#39;Thee Black Boltz&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2。“磁”</strong><br /> <strong>3。&#39;吃了月亮&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>4。&#39;pinstack&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>5。&#39;D