-survey-on-bullying-and-harassment-survey-3619290">新的调查，以应对音乐行业的欺凌和骚扰</a>，并得到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nova-twins">Nova Twins</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vv-brown">VV Brown</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kamille">Kamille</a>等人的支持。</p><p>他们还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-artists-and-promoters-in-london-face-nightlife-licensing-discrimination-say-black-lives-in-music-3793897">告诉伦敦议会，首都的理事会和警察在其许可决定中遵循“种族主义叙述”</a> 。博蒙特（Beaumont）在去年9月在伦敦经济，文化和技能委员会举行的伦敦夜生活中发表讲话时提出了索赔。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/black-lives-in-music-call-for-government-action-on-bullying-and-harassment-in-uk-music-its-rife-in-all-genres-3832663">《黑色邮报》在音乐中生活呼吁政府对英国音乐中的欺凌和骚扰行动：“所有流派的盛行”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Lady Gaga将新专辑“ Mayhem”描述为“ Utter Chaos” https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-describes-new-album-mayhem-as-utter-chaos-3832657?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lady-gaga-describes-new-album-混乱的菜Aneesa AhmedTue, 28 Jan 2025 19:33:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3832657 <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="嘎嘎小姐。信用 - 凯文·马祖尔（Kevin Mazur）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她说，它的影响来自“电垃圾，王子和鲍伊旋律，时髦的低音线条和法国电子舞”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-describes-new-album-mayhem-as-utter-chaos-3832657">Lady Gaga帖子将新专辑“ Mayhem”描述为“ Utter Chaos”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="嘎嘎小姐。信用 - 凯文·马祖尔（Kevin Mazur）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga.-Credit-Kevin-Mazur-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Lady Gaga在新的采访中将她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-announces-new-album-mayhem-3832317">即将发行的专辑“ Mayhem”</a>描述为“ Myhem”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/joker-folie-a-deux-review-lady-gaga-3790522"><b>“ Joker：FolieàDeux”评论：Lady Gaga在挑衅性的监狱音乐剧中闪耀</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手在唱片发行前与<a href="https://www.elle.com/culture/music/a63324386/lady-gaga-mayhem-interview-2025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Elle</em></a> Magazine进行了交谈，就类型而言，它将其描述为“完全混乱”  - 说它的影响来自“ 90年代替代品，Electro Grunge，Prince，Prince and Bowie Melodies，吉他和吉他，吉他和态度，时髦的低音线条，法国电子舞蹈和模拟合成器。”</p><p> “ [专辑]对我来说感觉很好。听起来不错。它打破了很多规则，并有很多乐趣。”她告诉媒体。</p><p>在谈到能够将音乐视为颜色的时，她说的是联合觉，她说：“当我写作时，它在我的大脑中组装，然后通过录音变成了完整的颜色。每首歌都是不同的阴影。这张专辑中的许多歌曲都有栗色的棕色。 “不好的浪漫”就是这样 - 它是红色的。”</p><p>加加还说，她以前以为是她的舞台角色和角色制作了音乐。但是，在使“混乱”的过程中，她释放了它来自内部； “我是创造者，我全力以赴，这帮助我以更深入的方式珍视自己是一名音乐家和词曲作者。” </p><figure id="attachment_3832329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Lady Gaga&#39;Mayhem&#39;专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lady-Gaga-Mayhem-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832329" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga&#39;Mayhem&#39;专辑艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><p>“ Mayhem”将是Gaga的第七张录音室专辑，可<a href="https://www.ladygaga.com/us-en/shop/collections/mayhem" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。由Gaga，Michael Polansky和Andrew Watt执行制作的14个曲目以及诸如Cirkut和Gesaffelstein之类的制片人的特色，“ Mayhem”已被保证会重新发明Gaga的“以羽衣甘蓝镜方法的早期声音”，如新闻稿一样。</p><p> Gaga的未婚夫Polansky也与<em>Elle</em>谈到了即将到来的项目。 “这张专辑看着她的制作真是太有趣了……令我最惊讶的是她的速度有多快。我简直不敢相信一首歌会多快。在五分钟之内，这首歌中有80％的人一无所有。”</p><p> Gaga将在2月2日在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">2025年格莱美奖</a>的商业休息期间首次亮相“混乱”的第三首单曲及其随附的音乐视频。</p><p>在其他新闻中，加加（Gaga）被确认为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">Coachella 2025的头条新闻，与Post Malone和Green Day一起</a>。她还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billie-Eilish">Billie Ei</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billie-Eilish">Lish</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Stevie-Nicks">Stevie Nicks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Green-Day">Green Day</a>等人一起参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-lady-gaga-green-day-stevie-nicks-and-more-to-perform-at-la-wildfires-benefit-concert-3829759">LA Wildfires Benefit Concert的表演者之一</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-describes-new-album-mayhem-as-utter-chaos-3832657">Lady Gaga帖子将新专辑“ Mayhem”描述为“ Utter Chaos”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
