ges的照片）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sleigh-Bells-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sleigh-Bells-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sleigh-Bells-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sleigh-Bells-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sleigh-Bells-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sleigh-Bells-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Sleigh-Bells">Sleigh Bells</a>分享了他们怀旧的新单曲“ Wanation Staend启动乐队？”并分享了美国巡回演出的细节。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sleigh-bells-texis-review-3044574">雪橇铃 - “德州”评论：纽约人摆脱了合规的束缚</a></strong></li></ul><p>怪异的曲目中有一系列噪音，尖锐的吉他和歌词，例如： <em>“二十年前的视觉踢 /正好像九十六个 /我曾经想过的梦想 /你想和我一起开始乐队吗？”</em>在雪橇铃的早期作为二人组。</p><p>根据乐队分享的声明，歌手亚历克西斯·克劳斯（Alexis Krauss）说：“在2008年，当时在布鲁克林的一家餐厅和我的妈妈，我们的服务器德里克（Derek）在布鲁克林的一家餐厅吃饭时，很少浪费时间问我，本质上是，&#39;基本上想着一支乐队吗？”。很难相信近17年后，我们仍然被大肆宣传，并沉迷于记录。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="雪橇铃 - 想开始乐队吗？ （官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0RXiWCkX_1Q?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她继续说：“德里克（Derek）在2014年左右开始与这首歌的即兴演奏弄乱 - 需要大量工作，但火花在那里。那时我们有一个乐队，但不知道它会持续多久。对我们来说，这首歌提醒我们我们的开始是如何开始的，但这也是我们想讲述的新故事的第一部分 - 更加详细介绍！”</p><p>随着“想启动乐队？”，雪橇铃还分享了他们即将举行的美国巡演的细节。一连串的日期将于5月7日在亚利桑那州凤凰城的新月宴会厅举行演出。 From there, the duo will make their way across the US with stops in cities such as San Fransisco, Seattle, Denver, Dallas, Austin, Tampa, Orlando, Philadelphia, Washington DC, Boston, New York, Chicago and more. The tour will wrap up on June 15 at the Majestic Theatre in Madison, Wisconsin.</p><p>通用门票销售将于周五（1月31日）当地时间上午10点开始。在下面查看巡回演出的完整列表，然后访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fsleigh-bells-tickets%2Fartist%2F1410738" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFX7ajluZHc/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C52